### How to build all Impulse Response Function (IRF) 

All simulations and ploting are done in Matlab (2025b, but can work with other versions). and with dynare version 6.5.

Need to : addpath('functions');


# Figure 4, 6, A.1, A.2
in folder fixed run: run_all.m

# Figure 5
in main folder, run [Plot_n_Compare_IRFs_fi](Plot_n_Compare_IRFs_fixed_vs_variable_Nimrod_2026_03_01.m)